CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 5, 1967, pg. 14 reads: "Five Generations - Little Latisha Eloise Henderson (seated on lap of great-great grandmother, Mrs. Mary Rowland) made the fifth generation represented in family pictured here. On Mrs. Rowland's left is her daughter Mrs. Jeannette Henderson, on the right is Mrs. Henderson's daughter Mrs. Eloise Grace of Philadelphia. In the rear are Mrs. Grace's son Preston and his wife Mildred Henderson.  The reunion took place at Mrs. Rowland's home on Elmore Sq., Pittsburgh. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Preston Henderson, standing with wife Mildred Henderson, holding Latisha Eloise Henderson outside of home of Mary Rowland, Elmore Square
